Package: tmap
License: GPL-3
Title: Thematic Maps
Type: Package
LazyLoad: yes
Authors@R: c(
	person("Martijn", "Tennekes", email="mtennekes@gmail.com", role=c("aut", "cre")),
	person("Joel", "Gombin", email="joel.gombin@gmail.com", role="ctb"),
	person("Kent", "Russell", email="kent.russell@timelyportfolio.com", role="ctb"))
Description:Thematic maps are geographical maps in which statistical data are visualized. This package offers a flexible, layer-based, way to create thematic maps, such as choropleths and bubble maps. Note: this version is without OSM and SVG features.
Version: 1.1
Date: 2015-07-15
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0),
    sp,
    raster
Imports:
    grid,
    gridBase,
    rgdal,
    rgeos,
    classInt,
    RColorBrewer
Suggests:
    knitr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
